{"tid":320220,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發火了！范冰冰提告郭文貴，表明「我不是妓女」","createTime":"2017-07-13T11:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-14T04:20:01.000Z","uid":41351,"like":13,"dislike":60,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"25f4dffb02d217ac43fd0e3f27630e7af77b264a","tid":320220,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:27:02.000Z","msg":"流亡美國的大陸富豪郭文貴日前爆料中共中紀委書記王岐山與多名女星發生過性關係，其中包括范冰冰，並稱兩人是透過春晚結緣，爆料一出，范冰冰霸氣回擊：「我就站在陽光下等你」，如今更透過工作室發出聲明，將對郭文貴提出訴訟。<br />\n  郭文貴先前大爆范冰冰已經被王岐山睡過，而范冰冰也在微博回嗆：「我就站在陽光下等著你，等你從黑暗裡走出來與我對峙！我從不缺少面對黑暗的勇氣！從前是，現在是！將來亦然！」引來不少粉絲紛紛轉發力挺。<br />\n  今（13）日范冰冰工作室更在微博發聲明，指控郭文貴透過境外個別媒體，發布一系列不實言論，惡意誹謗范冰冰，范冰冰已委託美國的律師事務所全權代理，將正式起訴郭文貴，並要求郭文貴和相關平台立刻停止散布、轉載不實訊息。<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=272532\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D272532&d=NKD3HVe32dgFiMQMoxBcMG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=0343ea95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D272532&h=a31e72e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=272532</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/13/192626_5fb0f654276c7da1e6357524bf78413a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F13%2F192626_5fb0f654276c7da1e6357524bf78413a.jpg&h=9ed8c9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武媚娘今次發火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d8b2393c93c3110c095eb92d564bb1de8dd905","tid":320220,"uid":37528,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:31:52.000Z","msg":"唔告正契弟"},{"pid":"bded3538835c1018737c13165e6d331c6efdd6fc","tid":320220,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T11:32:09.000Z","msg":"邊度有講'我不是妓女'？"},{"pid":"04093e713271f4eec884c8229107f15838e6e2c1","tid":320220,"uid":22251,"like"